ZH: 我每天坐巴士上学。
EN: I take the bus to school every day.

ZH: 这辆巴士太挤了，我找不到位置坐。
EN: This bus is too crowded, I can't find a seat.

ZH: 昨天的巴士晚点了一个小时。
EN: The bus was delayed for an hour yesterday.

ZH: 我习惯坐顶层的巴士。
EN: I prefer sitting on the top deck of the bus.

ZH: 坐巴士比开车省钱。
EN: Taking the bus is cheaper than driving.

ZH: 我下班后总是赶不上最后一班巴士。
EN: I always miss the last bus after work.

ZH: 他在等巴士的时候手机丢了。
EN: He lost his phone while waiting for the bus.

ZH: 巴士站离我的家很近。
EN: The bus stop is very close to my house.

ZH: 这个城市的巴士服务非常方便。
EN: The bus service in this city is very convenient.

ZH: 车站附近有一家卖巴士票的小店。
EN: There is a small shop near the station that sells bus tickets.

ZH: 我的巴士卡里没有钱了，需要充值。
EN: There is no money in my bus card, I need to recharge it.

ZH: 请不要在巴士上喧哗。
EN: Please do not make noise on the bus.

ZH: 换乘巴士的时候要小心保管好行李。
EN: Be careful to keep your luggage safe when transferring buses.

ZH: 这辆巴士的空调坏了。
EN: The air conditioning on this bus is broken.

ZH: 巴士到站前请按铃。
EN: Please ring the bell before the bus arrives at the stop.

ZH: 昨天的巴士司机很礼貌并且开车很稳。
EN: The bus driver yesterday was polite and drove smoothly.

ZH: 每次坐巴士都要检查一下座位上有没有留东西。
EN: Always check the seat for any belongings before getting off the bus.

ZH: 坐巴士可以减少交通拥堵。
EN: Taking the bus can reduce traffic congestion.

ZH: 我要等下一趟巴士才能回家。
EN: I have to wait for the next bus to go home.
